Nette-TweetButton (c) 2011 Tomáš Nedvìd (http://programator.ne2d.cz)



Introduction
------------

Nette Control for adding Tweet Button to your page

Twitter resources: http://twitter.com/about/resources/tweetbutton
Nette Framework homepage: http://www.nette.org/


Requirements
------------

- PHP (version 5 or better)
- Nette Framework


Usage
-----

Create factory

    public function createComponentTweetButton($name)
    {
      $tb = new Twitter_TweetButton($this, $name);
      return $tb;
    }

Create widget

    {widget tweetButton}

    
